# 🇮🇹 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Italy Readiness

This folder contains the official readiness brief and rollout strategy for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II expansion into Italy.

📄 [Download Italy Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Italy_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 📌 Key Highlights

- GDPR enforcement by Garante per la Protezione dei Dati Personali
- EU AI Act alignment under national innovation and health policy frameworks
- National Recovery and Resilience Plan (PNRR) funding digital health innovation
- Regionalized health governance supports pilot deployment
- Required localization into Italian; English accepted in pilot demos

---

## 🏛️ Governance & Innovation Partners

- Ministry of Health – Italy
- AGENAS – National Agency for Regional Health Services
- Garante per la Protezione dei Dati Personali (Italian DPA)
- Servizio Sanitario Nazionale (SSN)
- Regional health authorities: Lazio, Lombardy, Tuscany

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization

| Language  | Role |
|-----------|------|
| **Italian** | ✅ Required for public deployment and dashboards |
| **English** | ✅ Allowed in demo presentations and pilot documentation only |

🟢 Dual-version pilot kits available in Italian + English for stakeholder review.

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload the PDF readiness brief
- Begin outreach to AGENAS and Ministry of Health
- Localize compliance dashboards and AI audit tools in Italian
